---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="Terms and Conditions - Legacy Window Tint"
    description="Terms and Conditions for Legacy Window Tint's window tinting services in Arizona. Read our service terms, warranty conditions, and customer agreements."
>
    <!-- Legal Content Section -->
    <section class="legal-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="legal-content">
                <h1>Terms and Conditions</h1>
                <p class="last-updated"><strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 1, 2025</p>

                <h2>1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
                <p>By engaging Legacy Window Tint ("Company," "we," "us," or "our") for window tinting services, you ("Customer," "you," or "your") agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.</p>

                <h2>2. Services</h2>
                <p>Legacy Window Tint provides professional window tinting services for residential applications throughout Maricopa County, Arizona. Our services include:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Residential window film installation</li>
                    <li>Window tint removal services</li>
                    <li>Consultation and estimates</li>
                    <li>Mobile installation services</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>3. Pricing and Payment</h2>
                <p>All prices are quoted based on window size, number of windows, and complexity of installation. Payment is due upon completion of services unless other arrangements have been made in writing. We accept cash, credit cards, and electronic payments.</p>

                <h2>4. Warranty</h2>
                <p>We provide a warranty on our window films against:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Peeling, bubbling, or adhesion failure</li>
                    <li>Fading or discoloration under normal use</li>
                    <li>Cracking of the film</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Warranty does not cover damage caused by accidents, improper care, or damage occurring after installation. Warranty is non-transferable and applies only to the original customer.</p>

                <h2>5. Installation Process</h2>
                <p>Installation time varies depending on project size. Customers must allow proper curing time before cleaning windows. We are not responsible for pre-existing window damage discovered during installation.</p>

                <h2>6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
                <p>Our total liability for any claims related to our services shall not exceed the amount paid for the specific service. We are not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.</p>

                <h2>7. Property Condition</h2>
                <p>Customer represents that their property is in good condition and free from damage that could affect installation. Any pre-existing damage should be disclosed before service begins.</p>

                <h2>8. Cancellation Policy</h2>
                <p>Appointments may be cancelled or rescheduled with at least 24 hours notice. Same-day cancellations may be subject to a service fee.</p>

                <h2>9. Legal Compliance</h2>
                <p>Customer is responsible for ensuring their window tint meets local and state legal requirements. We provide guidance on Arizona tint laws but final compliance is the customer's responsibility.</p>

                <h2>10. Governing Law</h2>
                <p>These terms are governed by Arizona state law. Any disputes shall be resolved in the courts of Maricopa County, Arizona.</p>

                <h2>11. Changes to Terms</h2>
                <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Updated terms will be posted on our website with the revision date.</p>

                <h2>12. SMS Terms and Conditions</h2>

                <h3>12.1 Program Name and Description</h3>
                <p><strong>Legacy Window Tint SMS Program</strong></p>
                <p>By opting in, you will receive appointment reminders, quote follow-ups, promotional offers, and updates about window tinting services from Legacy Window Tint.</p>

                <h3>12.2 How to Opt-Out</h3>
                <p>You can cancel the SMS service at any time. Simply text "STOP" to the number. Upon sending "STOP," we will confirm your unsubscribe status via SMS. Following this confirmation, you will no longer receive SMS messages from us. To rejoin, sign up as you did initially, and we will resume sending SMS messages to you.</p>

                <h3>12.3 Help/Support</h3>
                <p>If you experience issues with the messaging program, reply with the keyword HELP for more assistance, or reach out directly to <a href="mailto:getlegacytint@gmail.com">getlegacytint@gmail.com</a> or call <a href="tel:8888875897">(888) 887-5897</a>.</p>

                <h3>12.4 Carrier Liability</h3>
                <p>Carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages.</p>

                <h3>12.5 Message and Data Rates</h3>
                <p>As always, message and data rates may apply for messages sent to you from us and to us from you. Message frequency varies. For questions about your text plan or data plan, contact your wireless provider.</p>

                <h3>12.6 Privacy Policy</h3>
                <p>For privacy-related inquiries, please refer to our privacy policy: <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a></p>

                <h2>Contact Information</h2>
                <p>For questions about these Terms and Conditions, please contact us:</p>
                <p><strong>Legacy Window Tint</strong><br>
                Phone: (888) 887-5897<br>
                Email: getlegacytint@gmail.com<br>
                Location: Surprise, Arizona<br>
                Service Area: Maricopa County, Arizona</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Schema Markup -->
    <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "WebPage",
        "@id": "https://legacywindowtint.com/terms-and-conditions",
        "name": "Terms and Conditions - Legacy Window Tint",
        "description": "Terms and conditions for Legacy Window Tint's window tinting services including warranty terms, pricing policies, and customer agreements.",
        "url": "https://legacywindowtint.com/terms-and-conditions",
        "isPartOf": {
            "@type": "WebSite",
            "name": "Legacy Window Tint",
            "url": "https://legacywindowtint.com"
        },
        "about": {
            "@type": "LocalBusiness",
            "name": "Legacy Window Tint"
        },
        "dateModified": "2025-01-01",
        "inLanguage": "en-US"
    }
    </script>

    <!-- Add noindex meta tag -->
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" slot="head">
</Layout>

<style>
    .legal-section {
        padding: 80px 20px;
        background: var(--gray-50);
    }

    .legal-content {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: var(--white);
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }

    .legal-content h1 {
        color: var(--gray-900);
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
    }

    .last-updated {
        color: var(--gray-700);
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        font-size: 0.9375rem;
    }

    .legal-content h2 {
        color: var(--gray-900);
        margin: 30px 0 15px 0;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold);
        padding-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .legal-content h3 {
        color: var(--gray-900);
        margin: 20px 0 10px 0;
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .legal-content p {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--gray-800);
    }

    .legal-content ul {
        margin: 15px 0;
        padding-left: 30px;
    }

    .legal-content li {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--gray-800);
    }

    .legal-content a {
        color: var(--gold);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .legal-content a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .legal-section {
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }

        .legal-content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }

        .legal-content h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .legal-content h2 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .legal-content h3 {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
    }
</style>
